# Quadcopter Frame Design (25 cm Constraint)

## Objective
Design a lightweight quadcopter frame within 25 cm size limit.

## Design Approach
- X-configuration for stability
- Modular motor mounts (M3 screws)
- Weight reduction using cut-outs

## Tools Used
- Fusion 360

## Key Features
- Compact geometry
- Easy assembly
- Lightweight structure

## Future Improvements
- FEA for stress validation
- Vibration damping
